HEADWORD: Glary
<hw>Glar"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of a dazzling luster;
glaring; bright; shining; smooth.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Bright, crystal glass is <qex>glary</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Boyle.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Glasgow</ent>⟦br⟧
